      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUNSET VENDETTA (7) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish half a length away in second (22.93) behind Rippin' Pike at this track. Top chance in this line up. NOVEL (1) was in traffic and missed the frame in a Grade 5/6 at this track over 300m latest, finishing a 3.5 lengths fifth (17.88). Has Box 1 this time where she has two wins. Can measure up this time. CHIEF WIGGUM (6) turned in a moderate run last time when fifth at this track over 400m behind Rippin' Pike (23.36) in a Grade 6. Placed at his previous run. Expected to run well. IMPRESS BUGSY (2) cannot be written off despite a miss here at his latest outing.",
